      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/myself/self_limiting_beliefs/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;self-limiting-beliefs&#34;&gt;Self Limiting Beliefs.&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;I need to be best to enter a field.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;I need to learn and adapt according to the field and add something to it.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol start=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;My past results defines me.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;What i&amp;rsquo;am doing currently is gonna define me.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol start=&#34;3&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;I&amp;rsquo;am a slow learner and I need large amount of time to learn something.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;I&amp;rsquo;am the fastest learner and I need to focus to learn something.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
